Source: force-urandom
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9)
Maintainer: Andrew Ayer <agwa@andrewayer.name>
Standards-Version: 3.9.6

Package: force-urandom
Architecture: any
Depends: libforceurandom (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Tool to force the use of /dev/urandom instead of /dev/random
 force-urandom allows you to execute a command with all opens of
 /dev/random directed to /dev/urandom instead.  It uses LD_PRELOAD to
 accomplish this.
 .
 This package provides the force-urandom command.

Package: libforceurandom
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Tool to force the use of /dev/urandom instead of /dev/random - shared libraries
 force-urandom allows you to execute a command with all opens of
 /dev/random directed to /dev/urandom instead.  It uses LD_PRELOAD to
 accomplish this.
 .
 This package provides the LD_PRELOAD library.
